#                            **Task Manager App**

---

<div align="center">

A modern, feature-rich task management app with **multi-user profiles**, stunning themes, detailed analytics, and image export.  
Built completely with **vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. Fully client-side. Deploy instantly on **Vercel**.

ğŸ”— [Live Demo](https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/)

