---

## ğŸ“ **Support & Troubleshooting**

- **Reset app:** Clear browser localStorage  
- **JS required:** JavaScript must be enabled in browser  
- **Browsers:** Use up-to-date Chrome, Edge, Firefox, Safari  
- **Console:** For errors, open browser developer console  

**Known Limitations**
- Storage: limited by browser (~5â€“10MB per user)
- No cloud/data sync (local only)
- Image export clarity relies on browser

